# Personal data — exclude from public repository
# These files contain personal life data and are specific to the original user.
# New users generate their own versions via the `start` command.

# Personal life arc (generated per-user by the start command)
Life-Arc-Overview.md
Life-Arc-Overview-*.md
# Public example structure (ship this); negation must follow the rule above
!Life-Arc-Overview-TEMPLATE.md

# Intellectual / side project list (personal; fill from template after clone)
System/Project-Tracker.md

# Weekly and monthly tracking logs (personal data)
System/Progress-Log.md
System/Progress-Visualizations.md
System/Role-Compass-Log.md
System/Reflections-Log.md

# Monthly plan files (personal; auto-generated each month)
System/Monthly-Plans/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-*.md

# Historical data (personal records)
System/Data/monthly-history/*.json
System/Data/monthly-history/*.ndjson

# App-specific project files (personal)
System/App-Project/

# Notion setup guide (contains personal workspace IDs if configured)
System/Notion-MCP-Setup-Guide.md

# Workspace file (IDE-specific, not needed for replication)
System/Life Building.code-workspace

# Personal curriculum docs
*.docx

# OS files
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor files
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
